<br>
I've been going to ToV alot in the HoT (assuming your cov alligned) best is to stick to fr + cr resists. My normal setup is for tov (resists stuff):<br>
<br>
froggy crown<br>
2 bd earings<br>
bd necklace<br>
diamond mask<br>
2 velium diamond rings<br>
<br>
With all my other equip it gets me to 220 fr + 200 cr, but the main bunch of resist comes from the above. Also if you have a runewood shield (15 fr) from the PoH might be worth bringing that along. From what i can see your equipment seems fine .. although maybe get some coldain skin boots if your looking for a 'general' upgrade for that slot? Though might be a waste of money as from what ive seen, leather boots are pretty common. Verm bracers also own for this place :) <p>Maani<br>
